{"id": "1471103215138242853", "channel_id": "1471103215138242853", "type": 0, "author_id": "191643200950239232", "author_name": "jadlithon", "author_bot": false, "content": "Continuation of the previous thread here for the post hotfix changes:\nhttps://discord.com/channels/1131791637933199470/1470345929537097728\n\nThe effect \"Motion Vertigo\" is incorrectly applying to Salvador's \"Dedication\" mode on his Suffering's End, as well as to his furnace gain from Defense and Blessed be the Bones.\n\nAdditionally, starting this patch, the Ultra Turn penalty also applies here.\n\nThe reason these are errors is because they also apply to when the furnace is used to heal - this means that the penalties are double dipping on Salvador's healing (which is why he is normally only affected by Healing Bonus rather than penalties to these values)", "timestamp": "2026-02-11T11:18:58.265000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2026-02-11T11:19:21.907000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1471103215972913217", "filename": "image.png", "content_type": "image/webp", "size": 165840, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1471103215138242853/1471103215972913217/image.png?ex=69ff1822&is=69fdc6a2&hm=174570eac27ab3abe12479b69c1e9916089952032b1bcef915e4046c6e18587d&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1471103215138242853", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「Answered」Salvador Bug with Train and Ultra Turn", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1181168103141416960", "1361168893200044183"]}
